Installation instructions:

npvrcop: type make. Dependencies: lapack and gfortran. In Fedora these can be installed with: yum install lapack-devel.x86_64 gcc-gfortran.x86_64
  
monitor.py: none. Dependencies: python, gnuplot, gnuplot-py. In Fedora these can be installed with: yum install python gnuplot gnuplot-py 

monitor2.py: none. Dependencies: python, matplotlib. In Fedora these can be installed with: yum install python2-matplotlib

fep1d.py: none. Dependencies: python, gnuplot, gnuplot-py.

